data.description: Charming 3 bed, 2 bath, 1700 sq. ft. home on Brenham Drive, one-story home located just off the main park area. History Maker Homes build with a wood-burning fireplace, 9' ceilings, granite countertops, espresso cabinets, large kitchen island, Whirlpool appliances, dual sink in master, garden tub & shower, full irrigation. Living in the Heartland community comes with fantastic amenities that cater to various interests including multiple pools, clubhouse, fitness center, parks, walking trails, basketball courts and a new elementary school just a 5-minute walk away. Convenient access to major roadways ensures that you're never too far from work, school, shopping, or entertainment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your dream home!
